', '
', "\item The side $\overline{AB}$ of triangle $ABC$ is extended and an altitude to the vertex $C$ is drawn, as shown below. The triangle's height is $h=4.8$ and its base measures $AB=7.1$. Find the area of the triangle.
", '\begin{flushright}
