', '
', '
', '
', '\newpage
', '
', '\item On the set of axes below, $\triangle ABC$ has vertices at $A(-2,0)$, $B(2,4)$, $C(4,-2)$, and $\triangle DEF$ has vertices at $D(4,0)$, $E(-4,8)$, $F(-8,-4)$.
